        public void turnTurret​(DriveDirections dir)
        Turn the turret.
        Parameters:
        dir - The direction to turn in. Only use DriveDirections.LEFT or DriveDirections.RIGHT. Any other value will stop the shooter.

      • preciseTurret

        public void preciseTurret​(double power,
                          DriveDirections dir)
        Turns the turret at a given speed.
        Parameters:
        power - The power to turn the shooter at. This should be positive, regardless of the direction to turn in.
        dir - The direction to turn in. This should be either DriveDirections.LEFT or DriveDirections.RIGHT. Anything else will stop the shooter.
